NK040(thi)010:1: // lcags khang bskul pa che ba ni /
NK040(thi)010:2: h'uh ma cig jo mo lab sgron ma //
NK040(thi)010:3: gnyan sa ri khrod bsgrod pa'i dus //
NK040(thi)010:4: khro mo sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba chen po la //
NK040(thi)010:5: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ma //
NK040(thi)010:6: nyi zla dmar nag 'dres pa'i hur gyis gzigs //
NK040(thi)010:7: zhal nas mche ba gangs ri ltar du gtsigs //
NK040(thi)010:8: shang nas h'u gi klu len kyu ru ru //
NK040(thi)010:9: dbu skra me 'bar steng gi lha gnas sleb //
NK040(thi)010:10: ye shes lnga yi tsh+wa tsh+wa spungs se spung //
NK040(thi)010:11: phyag g.yas rdo rje lcags kyu khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)010:12: tha thang brdab pa'i lha srin sde brgyad snying nas zungs //
NK040(thi)010:13: g.yon pa'i gnam lcags tho ba si li li //
NK040(thi)010:14: lha 'dre pho mo thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK040(thi)010:15: sku stod mi lpags khrag 'dzag gsol //
NK040(thi)010:16: khrag chen gyi thig le lhubs se lhub //
NK040(thi)010:17: thod rlon lnga bcu'i do shal byas //
NK040(thi)010:18: sku smad stag gi sham thabs byas //
NK040(thi)010:19: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum lcags khang gdan la bzhugs //
NK040(thi)010:20: ba spu'i smin mtshams thams cad la //
NK040(thi)010:21: h'u gis char pa si li li //
NK040(thi)010:24: kun kyang h'u sgra ti ri ri //
NK040(thi)010:26: rdo rje'i lcags kyu srangs se srang //
NK040(thi)010:27: gnam lcags tho ba sha ra ra //
NK040(thi)010:28: rdo rje khyung gi mda' 'phen sha ra ra //
NK040(thi)010:29: rdo rje thogs 'dril ser ba khra la la //
NK040(thi)010:30: rak+ta khrag gis char pa si li li //
NK040(thi)010:31: byin rlabs ye shes na bun thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)010:32: mtshon cha sna tshogs go ra khrigs se khrig /
NK040(thi)010:33: khros ma nag mo gur khang kyi li li //
NK040(thi)010:34: khyung dmar me 'bar gyi gshog brdung khrigs se khrig /
NK040(thi)010:35: mi nag lag sbrel gur khang skangs se skang //
NK040(thi)010:36: ral gri lo ma'i nags tshal shigs si shig /
NK040(thi)010:37: rgya stag ngar ma gram khrod spungs se spung //
NK040(thi)010:38: seng+ge rgya stag gur dang lhangs se lhang //
NK040(thi)010:39: mun pa nag po'i gur khang thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)010:40: ye shes bskal pa'i me ri phyi rim 'bar //
NK040(thi)010:41: mdze pho mdze mo'i gur ni nyi li li //
NK040(thi)010:42: steng nas rdo rje'i char pa 'bab pa la //
NK040(thi)010:43: 'og nas khrag gi rgya mtsho ma ra bsgom //
NK040(thi)010:44: zhabs nas lcags khang dmar nag 'ongs se 'ong //
NK040(thi)010:45: nang du gdon mgo bskor rjes snyog byed pa'i lha 'dre dang //
NK040(thi)010:46: dam nyams gnod byed thams cad nang du tshud //
NK040(thi)010:47: dbang du bsdus shig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)010:48: zil gyis gnon zhig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)010:49: dam la thog cig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)010:50: gnyan sa 'di la gnas pa'i lha 'dre rnams //
NK040(thi)010:51: ji srid sangs rgyas byang chub ma thob bar //
NK040(thi)010:52: khro mo chen mos zil gyi gnon par mdzod //
NK040(thi)010:54: mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag pa gal che'o //
NK040(thi)010:56: 'og lcags khang nag po'i gdan steng nas //
NK040(thi)010:57: pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan steng du //
NK040(thi)010:58: sprul pa'i sku mchog lab sgron ma //
NK040(thi)010:59: khros pa'i sku mdog dmar mo sprul //
NK040(thi)010:60: zhal gdangs snyan pa'i h'u sgra sgrogs //
NK040(thi)010:61: khrag gis thig le sku la brgyan //
NK040(thi)010:62: 'khor yang khros ma grangs med bskor //
NK040(thi)010:63: mi lpag g.yang gzhi phyar ba stong gis bskor //
NK040(thi)010:64: mi rkang gling bu 'bud pa stong gis bskor //
NK040(thi)010:65: zhing chen khur ba stong gis bskor //
NK040(thi)010:66: thod dbyug khur ba stong gis bskor //
NK040(thi)010:67: ma mkha' 'gro'i dmag dpung dbang bsdus la //
NK040(thi)010:68: khros ma nag mos dmag sna khrid //
NK040(thi)010:69: rje btsun dmar mo'i dmag dpung bskyed //
NK040(thi)010:70: bka' dang dam las 'da' mi rnams //
NK040(thi)010:71: grub thob gcod la mi nyan pa //
NK040(thi)010:72: zab mo chos kyi 'brel ba mi byed pa //
NK040(thi)010:73: dam pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo mi bskor pas //
NK040(thi)010:74: lha srin sde brgyad thams cad rnams //
NK040(thi)010:75: lcags khang nag po'i nang du tshud //
NK040(thi)010:76: mi lpags dmar pos kha khob cig /
NK040(thi)010:77: mi mgo phreng bas mtha' non zhig /
